# The format of this file is identical to `.dockerignore`.
# It is used to reduce the size of deployed images to make the process of publishing faster.
# Production only needs: api-server + tawbah-web (web bundle served as static files).

# ── Replit internals ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.local

# ── pnpm store (already installed, no need to ship the cache) ─────────────────
.local/share/pnpm
**/.pnpm-store
.pnpm-store

# ── Mobile app — not needed in production web deployment ─────────────────────
artifacts/tawbah-mobile
artifacts/tawbah-mobile-backup

# ── Capacitor Android project — only used for APK builds, not web serving ────
artifacts/tawbah-web/android

# ── Mockup / design sandbox — dev-only ───────────────────────────────────────
artifacts/mockup-sandbox

# ── Build caches & Gradle ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.gradle
**/.gradle
**/build/intermediates
**/build/generated
**/build/tmp

# ── node_modules (reinstalled during build) ───────────────────────────────────
# Keep api-server node_modules to speed up cold starts; exclude heavy packages
artifacts/tawbah-web/node_modules
artifacts/tawbah-mobile/node_modules
artifacts/tawbah-mobile-backup/node_modules
artifacts/mockup-sandbox/node_modules

# ── Dev / docs / large non-essential files ────────────────────────────────────
attached_assets
screenshots
docs
*.zip
*.apk
*.aab
f.txt
tawbah-web-apk.zip
pnpm-lock.yaml.323642236
APP_MEMORY.md
MOBILE_MIGRATION_PLAN.md
QURAN_ROADMAP.md
zakiy_full_analysis.md
store-listing.md
Tawbah-Ai.md
"Proposed plan.md"
www.youtube.com_watch_v=Ts_A8TwE9G0.png
